title: Mikrotik ROS: Wireless Clients
catalog: hw/network/mikrotik
agents: snmp
license: GPL
distribution: Techfu NMS
description:
 This check monitors the wireless clients connected.
 It uses SNMP to scan the {mtxrWlRtabTable} in the MIKROTIK.MIB.

item:
 Each client's MAC address.

inventory:
 The inventory creates a service for each cleint MAC address found connected.

 
